                    <span>INDIVIDUAL Home Owner vs SOCIETY wealth, as well as paper profits [unrealized] vs. actual [realized] profits, is the source of your confusion.<br /><br />While it is true that one INDIVIDUAL homeowner had actual [realized] profits, four INDIVIDUAL homeowners (SOCIETY) based on their (false) perception of value, end up with actual [realized] loses.<br /><br />One person &#39;wins&#39; and everyone else loses, as it should be ...?<br />I hesitate to ponder the implications that such a course of thought leads to... only the &#39;stupi</span>
                
            </div>

